  narr:Narrative_HallucinationHook

    dct:source      narr:Sample_1 ;
    narr:theme      "Trust is built by showing both what is grounded and what is ungrounded — the absence of citation is as important as its presence" ;
    skos:broader    narr:NarrativeAnchor ;
    skos:note       "The hallucination hook is not merely raising fear of hallucination; it promises a specific resolution: the annotate tool shows provenance AND flags ungrounded content. The hook that landed frames the trust binary as the differentiator." ;
