    narr:theme      "Tagline memorability vs. trust-mechanism clarity is audience-dependent: vision-oriented CEOs respond to 'think like your org'; ops leads and technical buyers respond to 'cited or flagged as ungrounded'" ;
    skos:broader    narr:NarrativeAnchor ;
    skos:note       "Open question: both versions should be retained for different audience contexts. The trust-mechanism version is clearer and more impactful in regulated or skeptical domains but is wordier." ;
    prov:wasGeneratedBy narr:Tx_20260310T234025Z .

