    skos:broader    narr:CoreNarratives ;
    skos:note       "The an early prospect call demonstrated a hybrid: read demo → interview → background memory extraction → deliver relevant output on the same call. The rigid Call One / Call Two framing may be too prescriptive. A third option should be captured in the TX." ;
    prov:wasGeneratedBy narr:Tx_20260310T234025Z .

